l CSM\ninteraction, while 17ahn-like Type IIL SNe come from a more massive progenitor\nwith less hydrogen in its envelope.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 May 2021 17:10:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-30"}
