-point subtraction, scale-dependent\nMetacalibration responses, PSF residuals, and B-modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 May 2021 01:58:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Apr 2022 19:46:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-11"}
