om cosmic\nshear by up to 31\\%, and for the full combination of probes (3$\\times$2pt) by\nup to 10\\%. The shear ratios presented in this work are used as an additional\nlikelihood for cosmic shear, 2$\\times$2pt and the full 3$\\times$2pt in the\nfiducial DES Y3 cosmological analysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 May 2021 01:58:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Apr 2022 19:39:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-11"}
