 scientific inquiry do not come with uncontrolled researcher degrees\nof freedom once confronted with a specific psycholinguistic datasets. We also\nintroduce a distinction between replicable and non-replicable non-linear\neffects. We conclude that GAMMs are an excellent and reliable tool for\nunderstanding experimental data, including chronometric data with time-varying\neffects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 May 2021 12:47:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Nov 2021 21:56:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-19"}
