 work\nindicates that {\\alpha}-Sn is an excellent model system to study novel\ntopological phases and a prominent material candidate for topological devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 May 2021 14:49:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-27"}
